Definition: any of various herbs of the genus Thalictrum
Example: sometimes rhizomatous or tuberous perennials found in damp shady places and meadows or stream banks; have lacy foliage and clouds of small purple or yellow flowers
Synonyms: wildflower, genus_Thalictrum, m, any, of, various, herbs, the, genus, Thalictrum, sometimes, rhizomatous, or, tuberous, perennials, found, in, damp, shady, places, and, meadows, stream, banks, have, lacy, foliage, clouds, small, purple, yellow, flowers
Category: noun.plant
